  "title": "Tax Senior",
  "description": "<p>Job Description &amp; Requirements</p>\n<ol>\n  <li>Perform review of account and compute estimated chargeable income for clients.</li>\n  <li>Prepare tax provisions for audit purposes based on draft account.</li>\n  <li>Work with auditors and clients to prepare the tax computation with supporting schedules and tax returns.</li>\n  <li>Submission of tax return and tax computation to the Inland Revenue Authority of Singapore.</li>\n  <li>Attend to tax queries issued by the Inland Revenue of Singapore.</li>\n  <li>Verify Notices of Assessment and advice clients to tax status and tax payment matters.</li>\n  <li>Assist Director in tax advisory matters.</li>\n  <li>Any ad-hoc projects.</li>\n  <li>Any other duties assigned by the Director.</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n  <li>Bachelor's degree in Accountancy, Finance, or a relevant field with professional certification.</li>\n  <li>Min 3 years of Singapore tax experience in a professional services or accounting firm</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skill.</li>\n  <li>Driven, able to work under pressure and meet deadline.</li>\n  <li>Committed to the profession and professional code of conduct.</li>\n  <li>Team player, yet has high level of initiative and integrity.</li>\n  <li>Organised, independent &amp; meticulous.</li>\n  <li>Ability to work independently.</li>\n</ul>",
